properties.areaDesc: Ventura County Coastal Valleys; Ventura County Interior Valleys
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 27 at 12:01PM PST until January 30 at 3:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Areas of north to northeast winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts
to 45 mph. Local gusts to 55 mph are possible in the hills late
Tuesday through Thursday.

* WHERE...Ventura County Interior Valleys and Ventura County
Coastal Valleys.

* WHEN...Until 3 PM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for drivers of high profile
vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power
outages may result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The strongest winds will be in the eastern
Ventura County Valleys, including Simi and Conejo Valleys, and
affecting Highways 101, 126, and 23.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 PM PST THURSDAY
